description: A colorful Icemule map hangs on one of the blue plaster walls, and an oak-framed ceiling rises overhead.  A polar bear rug sits in one corner of a golden blonde oak floor.  There is a lacquered wooden shelf on one side of the shop and a smooth plaster counter on the other.
title: [Kiyote's Weaponry]
[Kiyote's Outfitting]
